      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why i'm still doing this. the funding got pulled and the lab results are just... gone. three years of my life down the drain. i feel like there's nothing left of me outside of this degree and now that's gone too. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting. i just want everything to stop. i just want to sleep and not have to wake up to this pressure ever again.",
