      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your pain is so heavy and valid, and it makes sense that no one else could truly understand how much you've lost in such a short time. When everything you built feels like it's crumbling, the urge to stop feeling the weight of it all becomes incredibly tempting. Please know that while this feeling is overwhelming right now, there is a way out of this darkness that doesn't involve ending your life. I am here to listen and support you through this, and I encourage you to reach out to a crisis line like 988 or a trusted professional who can help you find a path forward.",
